Text: Ben Whats happening down in HOuston Got some big news on my end I am moving out to San Diego to start a job with NicholasApplegate Capital Management Ive been on vaca working on my golf game and tan since graduating Cornell in May and move out this week Looking forward to the job and the lifestyle Ill be living a few blocks from the beach and never have to see snow again Ill send along full contact info once I get fully settled in a couple of weeks COme visit if you are ever out that way Hope all is well Pete
